<plot>Shame is the story of Hawa, a young Pakistani woman, struggling to overcome the stigma of her childhood. As a child, Hawa was molested by an uncle and forced to endure the shame and guilt associated with sexual abuse. Now in her twenties, Hawa once again finds herself subjected to the humiliation and abuse that has haunted her since childhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?490350</url></doc>
